title: Zebra-Media Total Video Converter 1.9.0.0
description:
Zebra-Media Total Video Converter 1.9.0.0 | 27.0 MB

Zebra Total Video Converter is an easy-to-use tool to fast convert between various video/audio files. It supports a wide range of video and audio including AVI, MP4, WMV, MKV, MOV, MPG, RM, RMVB, 3GP, VCD, DVD, DV, Flash Video FLV, SWF, HD MP4, H.264, XviD/Divx, etc. and audio MP3, MP2, WMA, OGG, AAC, AC3, FLAC, WAV, RA between each other. It can also extract audio from video and adjust video effects like trim,crop, merge, hook and Watermark. It can customize video codec, height, width, Bit-rate, Frame-rate, NTSC/PAL,4:3/16:9/37:20/47:20 for outputs, cut movies into smaller clips and fully convert video to image JPEG. It will even extract audio tracks from video files and save them as audio files, which is handy for you to create mobile phone ring tones out of famous movies or TV songs. Zebra Total Video Converter can convert multiple files simultaneously with multi-threading and batch processing
